<%@ page contentType="text/html;charset=UTF-8" %><%@ taglib prefix="c" uri="http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/core" %><!doctype html><html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><title>Discharge Patient</title><link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"></head><body><%@ include file="/WEB-INF/views/common/header.jsp" %><main class="container py-4"><h1>Discharge <c:out value="${admission.admissionNumber}"/></h1><p><c:out value="${admission.patientName}"/> — admitted <c:out value="${admission.admissionDate}"/> — Room <c:out value="${admission.roomNumber}"/> / <c:out value="${admission.bedNumber}"/> at ₹<c:out value="${admission.dailyRate}"/> per day.</p><p>The server calculates final chargeable days and room charges.</p><form method="post"><input type="hidden" name="csrfToken" value="${sessionScope.csrfToken}"><input type="hidden" name="admissionId" value="${admission.admissionId}"><textarea class="form-control" name="dischargeSummary" maxlength="4000" placeholder="Discharge summary" required></textarea><label class="mt-3"><input type="checkbox" name="createOrUpdateBill"> Create or update final bill with room charge</label><input class="form-control mt-2" name="additionalRoomChargeDescription" maxlength="200" placeholder="Optional safe room-charge description"><button class="btn btn-success mt-3">Discharge Patient</button></form></main><%@ include file="/WEB-INF/views/common/footer.jsp" %></body></html>
